<h1>
    <h1 style="color: red;font-size: larger;font-family: 'Gill Sans', 'Gill Sans MT', Calibri, 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;">Consulting</h1>
    <h2>
Scope Tech Solution as a IT consulting company works with clients to help them solve IT problems. The field includes everything from basic network analytics assistance all the way up to managed IT solutions.

Most consulting firms will specialize in a fairly narrow field of IT. These can include: 
<ul>
    <li>CRM</li>
<li>Cyber Security</li>
<li>Digital Transformation</li>
<li>IT Service Management</li>
<li>Business Intelligence</li>
<li>Medical IT Consulting</li>
<li>Remote Work Consulting</li>
<li>Robotic Process Automation</li>
<li>Bigdata - DevOps</li>
</ul>
</h2>
